# .claudeignore

## OS files

.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

## Chess engines and testing tools

stockfish/
*.tar

## Git tracking

.git/

## Virtual environment

.venv/

## Python

__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo

## Ruff cache

.ruff_cache/

## External libraries (but allow Fathom submodule)

lib/*
!lib/Fathom/

## Syzygy tablebases

syzygy/
*.rtbw
*.rtbz

## Build output

build/

## Game PGN files

games/

## Polyglot opening books

books/
